{
  "verses": [
    {
      "number": "1",
      "arabic_text": "ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ",
      "translation": "1. Al-Qâri‘ah (the striking Hour i.e. the Day of Resurrection)."
    },
    {
      "number": "2",
      "arabic_text": "مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ",
      "translation": " 2. What is the striking (Hour)?"
    },
    {
      "number": "3",
      "arabic_text": "وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ",
      "translation": " 3. And what will make you know what the striking (Hour) is?"
    },
    {
      "number": "4",
      "arabic_text": "يَوۡمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلۡفَرَاشِ ٱلۡمَبۡثُوثِ",
      "translation": " 4. It is a Day whereon mankind will be like moths scattered about."
    },
    {
      "number": "5",
      "arabic_text": "وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ ٱلۡمَنفُوشِ",
      "translation": " 5. And the mountains will be like carded wool."
    },
    {
      "number": "6",
      "arabic_text": "فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ",
      "translation": " 6. Then as for him whose balance (of good deeds) will be heavy,[1]"
    },
    {
      "number": "7",
      "arabic_text": "فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ",
      "translation": " 7. He will live a pleasant life (in Paradise)."
    },
    {
      "number": "8",
      "arabic_text": "وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ",
      "translation": " 8. But as for him whose balance (of good deeds) will be light,"
    },
    {
      "number": "9",
      "arabic_text": "فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٞ",
      "translation": " 9. He will have his home in Hâwiyah (pit, i.e. Hell)."
    },
    {
      "number": "10",
      "arabic_text": "وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهۡ",
      "translation": " 10. And what will make you know what it is?"
    },
    {
      "number": "11",
      "arabic_text": "نَارٌ حَامِيَةُۢ",
      "translation": " 11. (It is) a fiercely blazing Fire!"
    }
  ]
}